attributionInfo.brokerName: Douglas Elliman Real Estate - The Sarkis Team
Douglas Elliman Real Estate - The Sarkis Team

description: Echelon at its finest! Better than new w/$175K+ in upgrades. 2+ bed/2.5 bath home offers stunning harbor and Blue Hills views. A welcoming foyer leads to the bright living and dining areas, ideal for entertaining. The home features custom built-ins, a gorgeous bar with a Thermador wine fridge, a rare fireplace, and a bonus relaxation room (with a luxurious spa chair included!). The chef’s kitchen boasts sleek Italian cabinetry, top-tier appliances, and gas cooking. The serene bedrooms and spa-inspired baths come with custom closets for added luxury. Two valet parking spaces and a spacious private storage area are just steps away. 50,000+ sq ft of exclusive amenities, the club level includes a lounge, private dining, outdoor terraces w/grills, and fire pits. The Sky Lounge offers incredible skyline views, while the indoor & outdoor pools, hot tub, fitness center (indoor basketball court, sport simulator, & hot yoga studio) & spa facilities offer the ultimate in relaxation & recreation.
